      "title": "A traffic jam in Dematagoda",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Our reporters say that there is a heavy traffic queue from Dematagoda towards Borella due to heavy traffic near the Dematagoda petrol station.",
        "After a few days, there is a heavy traffic jam on the road due to the traffic coming to get fuel from the Dematagoda fuel station."
      ],
